{
  "schema": "2.0",
  "config": {"wide_screen_mode": true},
  "header": {
    "title": {"tag": "plain_text", "content": "🚀 {{version}} · {{env}} 发版通知"},
    "template": "wathet",
    "subtitle": {"tag": "plain_text", "content": "MLA · {{env}} · {{datetime}}"}
  },
  "body": {
    "elements": [
      {
        "tag": "column_set",
        "flex_mode": "trisect",
        "columns": [
          {"tag": "column", "elements": [{"tag": "div", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "<font color=grey>版本号</font>\n**{{version}}**"}}]},
          {"tag": "column", "elements": [{"tag": "div", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "<font color=grey>环境</font>\n<text_tag color='blue'>{{env}}</text_tag>"}}]},
          {"tag": "column", "elements": [{"tag": "div", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "<font color=grey>状态</font>\n<text_tag color='green'>✅ 已发好</text_tag>"}}]}
        ]
      },
      {"tag": "hr"},
      {
        "tag": "div",
        "text": {
          "tag": "lark_md",
          "content": ":Loudspeaker: **版本负责人知悉**\n<at id=\"ou_atlas\">王同乐(Atlas)</at>  <at id=\"ou_scott\">张超(Scott)</at>\n请知悉～"
        }
      },
      {"tag": "hr"},
      {
        "tag": "div",
        "text": {
          "tag": "lark_md",
          "content": ":OnIt: **活动配置请跟进**\n<at id=\"{{owner1_open_id}}\">{{owner1_name}}</at>  <at id=\"{{owner2_open_id}}\">{{owner2_name}}</at>\n麻烦配置活动，辛苦了！:THUMBSUP:"
        }
      },
      {"tag": "hr"},
      {
        "tag": "div",
        "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "<font color=grey>:DONE: {{version}} · {{env}} · 由 Claude Bot 自动发送</font>"}
      }
    ]
  }
}
